reviewText: Wonderful!!!  Just what I have been looking for -- my Father died last year and my Mother cannot watch any of the movies they used to watch together. Roy Rogers brings back happy memories of her childhood - it is just terrific to have this on VHS tape for her as she never mastered the DVD transition.

This DVD contains four episodes
The Set Up (1/20/52)
Phantom Rustlers (4/5/53)
Ambush (1/15/56)
Empty Saddles (3/10/56)
